author: Sandy Zh
text: Wonderful place to come with friends and family. Lovely atmosphere and wonderful service. Food is delicious! Thank you to Bota who made sure we had a great time and everything we needed! Loved everything about our evening at Lova Coffee!

author: Claire Sutton
text: I have just tried this restaurant and was very disappointed. First i order a small orange juice. They didnt have it, but insteaad of informing me this they decideed to bring me a large jug of lemonade with mint which i dont like. I ended up having water as no other cold drinks were actually available. I ordered chicken with spinach from the menu. There was no mention of mushroom in this dish. When the food arrived it was basically small chicken and spinach with a plate full of mushrooms. I dont like mushrooms. When i tried to complain all of a sudden no one understand English. If you go there do not expect to get what you order. I left withouut essting or drinking anything

text:
The waitress took away my full glass of lemonade while I was talking with my wife without my noticing it!
When I complained, they apologized and said that they will replace it, but instead, to my great SHOCK, they. only brought me a THIRD of a glass of lemonade!
Can you believe it? 
Not only are they SUPER CHEAP but they actually  stole my glass of lemonade, which I, of course, paid for!
